trans-unit.source: Provides access to the name/value pair of a custom (expando) attribute that was previously registered with the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Page"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 提供存取先前登錄的自訂 (expando) 屬性的名稱/值組<xref href="System.Web.UI.Page"></xref>物件。

trans-unit.source: Gets the control that registered the custom (expando) attribute.
trans-unit.target: 取得已註冊的自訂 (expando) 屬性的控制項。

trans-unit.source: A reference to the control that registered the custom attribute.
trans-unit.target: 註冊自訂屬性的控制項的參考。

trans-unit.source: Gets the identifier of the control that registered the custom (expando) attribute.
trans-unit.target: 取得控制項註冊自訂 (expando) 屬性的識別項。

trans-unit.source: The identifier of the control that registered the custom attribute.
trans-unit.target: 註冊的自訂屬性的控制項識別碼。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the custom (expando) attribute is encoded.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，指出是否要編碼的自訂 (expando) 屬性。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the custom attribute is encoded; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果編碼的自訂屬性;否則， <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the custom (expando) attribute.
trans-unit.target: 取得自訂 (expando) 屬性的名稱。

trans-unit.source: The name of the custom attribute.
Gets the value of the custom (expando) attribute.
trans-unit.target: 取得自訂 (expando) 屬性的值。

trans-unit.source: The value of the custom attribute.
